Forever 21 is proud to employ people of many diverse backgrounds and experiences. Through the hard work and vision of our talented team, we continue to be a place that welcomes and celebrates everyone. Please take a minute to listen to our #F21FAM talk about their culture, experiences and thoughts on the recent issues and events affecting the #AAPICommunity. 

We're sharing these conversations with the #F21Community to continue to raise awareness and we hope these conversations lead the way to self-reflection and healing. We also hope this provides you with some comfort and encouragement.

💛 Leave a comment below ➡️ share something about your culture that you love! 😍 #forevertogether❤ 

🎥: @cliffordwilliam
